divs: Sighting DetailsWalked outside to car at 7;15pm aprox when i saw hanging in the sky a large diamond shaped object with a red or white light at the top and the same on the bottom At least the size of a house hanging low in the sky over a residential area in South Salinas No sound no motion When i got into car to try and get closer I could no longer see it after parking My cae a few blocks away Another person i told of this sighting said they also saw something with their girlfriend in the Same aprox time and locatiion
Summary: Diamond shaped craft the size of house or larger hanging silently low in sky
